creator: Marietta Holley
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 10 recordings of Spring Song of the Swallow by Marietta Holley, (better known as Josiah Allen's Wife). This was the Weekly Poetry project for March 22, 2015, in honour of spring 2015! - (Summary by Rachel) Read in English by Caitlin Buckley; Ezwa; Greg Giordano; Ian King; J. McDougall; Lee Ann Howlett; Larry Wilson; Maria Kasper; Mary Ann Weathers and Rachel. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
